Rufus Griswold wanted some of Poe's poems in a book and convinced Poe that he  would become famous. Poe later read the book and all his poems were in the back of the book. Poe decided to talk to Griswold, when he did, the man wanted him to write a review about the book for a reward of $100. Poe decided to take the opportunity to get back at the man and wrote the worst review possible. He said the book was crap and that nobody would read it. I can look into it more later but I believe this man went insane and did horrible things to Poe.
